summary: The tree outside of Lakeview manor is now gone.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=Gold][size=15]Lakeview tree removal[/size][/color][/center] 
[line]
[center][color=Gold][size=4]by bwins95[/size][/color][/center] 
[color=Gold][size=3]Version             :[/size][/color]1.0
[color=Gold][size=3]Date                :[/size][/color]08/13/2012
[color=Gold][size=3]Category            :[/size][/color]Landscape changes
[line] 
This mod requires the Hearthfire DLC to work. 
[line] 

[u][center][size=5][color=Gold]Description[/color][/size][/center][/u] 
[center]The tree outside Lakeview manor has been bugging me, so I disabled it and now it it gone.[/center] 
[line]
